Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: Pastor Mark Harris will be a terrific Representative for North Carolina’s 8th Congressional District! As your next Congressman, Mark will work hard to Grow the Economy, Lower Inflation, Uphold the Rule of Law, Defend the Border, Promote American Energy, Support our Military and Police, and Protect our always under siege Second Amendment. Mark Harris has my Complete and Total Endorsement - HE WILL NOT LET YOU DOWN!
